.DT
monitor
Discworld player help
monitor

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
monitor - Hit point monitor.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
monitor [off|on|slow|snails pace]
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Monitor is a hit point monitor that goes on during combat.  This tells
you the current state of your hit points and guild points.  Monitor by
itself will show the current monitor status.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> monitor on
Your hit point monitor is set to on.
> monitor slow
Your hit point monitor is set to slow.
> monitor
Your hit point monitor is set to slow.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
health, score.
.EP
